INSERT INTO `wp_postmeta` VALUES("1737", "300", "add_interview_text", "The entire NFV evolution is ecosystem driven, where service providers are trying to establish vendor agnostic network architectures. A healthy ecosystem driven by partner collaboration is crucial for successful commercialization of these solutions, and for F5, working with a strong ecosystem partner like CloudBand is essential. We have had a very positive experience and customer driven collaboration with Alcatel-Lucent.  Working together, we are able to better deploy our solutions and put use cases in place for customers in a commercial environment. It is a matter of continuing to work with customers, understand what types of problems they want to solve, and what business models they want to pursue.  For F5 and Alcatel-Lucent to be successful working together, it is important for us to be cognizant of what the business objectives are for our customers and work together to help those customers succeed. It is a continuous process that will continue to evolve.");
