o deploy the VNF as well as rules for scaling and other lifecycle operations.\r\n\r\nIf one thing was obvious at the event, it was that NFV is here to stay and will fundamentally change the telecommunications industry. Vendors and service providers have started to transform themselves making cloud and NFV central to their infrastructures with new roles and responsibilities as well as new business models. See you next time at SDN &amp; OpenFlow", "NFV is hot at SDN & OpenFlow World Congress", "", "inherit", "open", "open", "", "318-revision-v1", "", "", "2015-07-22 18:18:05", "2015-07-22 18:18:05", "", "318", "http://ecosystem.cloud-band.com/2015/07/22/318-revision-v1/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
